##HTML: <p >{{#c}}</p>
msgid "\n"
"	Pietistic, amillennial and premillennial efforts lead invariably to a ret"
"reat from the world into a convent-type church which is made into a place of re"
"fuge from the world rather than a place of preparation for battle. Such churche"
"s emphasize songs of escapism, hymns that celebrate Christ as one who supposedl"
"y rescues them from the world and the problems of the world, they stress life o"
"n a “higher plane,” i.e., one of removal from the world’s battles."
